349
00:24:55,839 --> 00:24:57,920
[SPEAKER_01] Ali to nije bio dio u kojem sam se vratio na posao.

350
00:24:58,000 --> 00:24:59,680
[SPEAKER_01] Još sam imao šest mjeseci u slobodnom životu.

351
00:24:59,759 --> 00:25:00,079
[SPEAKER_01] U redu.

352
00:25:00,240 --> 00:25:00,640
[SPEAKER_01] U redu.

